Moved punctuation mark inside quotation marks because this matches WP style guidelines which states that if the quotation starts with a capital letter and includes one or more setences, the punctuation mark can be included within the quotation.

EcoTechnoPark - First sentence needs to be divided into two parts. Second sentence: "It is situated in...  and "it is called" [not they call it] because there is still no clarity over the origin of the name.

Removed boldface text from acronyms like CONFOB and EFSA; I checked Wikipedia style and it seems boldface should be avoided. Please advise on use of quotation marks in the lede for the company names. Is this the best way to introduce them?

Many national banks have issued financial warnings about SkyWay (we're still waiting confirmation on the Czech republic - see talk page). We can only list the verified countries but saying 'many countries including' better represents the truth.
Evaluation of the 'SkyWay' technology (removed of group, that refers to the companies and not the technology.

/* Scam */ rv addition to closed section. this is not a forum.
According to the reference they don't 'attempt' to sell the shares; they just sell them.
